text:
I was gone from my apartment from 8AM-10AM on a Monday morning and that's when @FedEx @FedExHelp came. 

Who is going to be home at that time? Basically nobody.

@Saul_Says Hello, this is Robin. I'm sorry we missed you. I will be happy to see what options are available for you. Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
